imageAssets.description: A vibrant, glossy, circular red food pellet icon, approximately 20x20 pixels. Simple, appealing, and clearly visible on a light gray background. Style: flat design with subtle highlights.
imageAssets.purpose: Food item for snakes. Fallback: draw red circle with canvas.

imageAssets.description: A small, simple, elegant golden crown icon. Minimalist design, clearly recognizable as a crown. Suitable to be drawn above a 20x20 snake head segment. Approx 15x10 pixels. Style: flat design icon, metallic gold color.
imageAssets.purpose: Visual indicator for the longest snake. Fallback: draw yellow triangle.

imageAssets.description: A set of 3-4 small, abstract 'sparkle' or 'burst' shapes for a particle effect. Yellow and orange colors. Individual shapes should be tiny (e.g., 5x5 pixels). The overall image can be a small spritesheet (e.g., 20x20) containing these shapes or just one iconic burst shape. Style: cartoonish, energetic.
imageAssets.purpose: Particle effect for food consumption or snake elimination. Fallback: draw small colored squares.
